<div id="banner">
	<h1>An Anti-DRM Video Game</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>In EFF&#8217;s continuing output of extremely innovative ways to get their message across, they&#8217;ve created <a href="http://www.eff.org/cafe/drmgame/">The Carabella Game: The Quest for Tunes</a>, a video game to teach people about fair use rights. The moral of the game is that there is no perfect solution here.</p>

